      "content": "i hear u but honestly im just super stressed. everything feels a bit heavy and my neck feels kind of stiff too, but maybe thats just from hunching over my books all day? i rly dont want to waste time in an ER if it's just stress/dehydration. if i take a really strong dose of ibuprofen and maybe some melatonin to just pass out and sleep through it, do u think that's a safe way to just reset my system for tomorrow?",
